[00:10.30]How long had the police taken to find his bicycle?|警察花了多长时间才找到他的自行车？
[00:16.58]Dan Robinson has been worried all week.|丹·罗宾逊整个星期都一直很担心。
[00:20.97]Last Tuesday he received a letter|上周二，他收到了一封信。
[00:23.82]from the local police.|来自当地警方。
[00:26.19]In the letter he was asked to call at the station.|在信中，他被要求去车站一趟。
[00:30.94]Dan wondered why|丹想知道为什么。
[00:32.54]he was wanted by the police,|他被警方通缉了。
[00:35.71]but he went to the station yesterday|但他昨天去车站了。
[00:38.53]and now he is not worried anymore.|现在他不再担心了。
[00:42.18]At the station,|在车站里，
[00:43.72]he was told by a smiling policeman|一位面带微笑的警察告诉了他这件事。
[00:46.81]that his bicycle had been found.|他的自行车已经被找到了。
